\cf2 \cb3 health outcomes, 8,500 new sta\uc0\u64256 , fair funding for mental health services, specialist mental health support in\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 every school, and an open access mental health hub for children and young people in every community.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 Labour will tackle the root cause of capacity challenges in the NHS with the most ambitious expansion of\cf0 \cb1 \
